\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T04:55:59.000Z","msg":"要講後期出果幾本殺手 得迴光返照的命運比較值得睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其他都真係麻麻地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T08:44:46.000Z","msg":"唔係後期嘅殺手唔好睇, 我直情覺得佢喺大約獵命師結局開始, 大部份小說都開始回塘, 係得已毒不悔叫高質返少少:<br />\n<br />\n獵命師吹太大埋唔到尾焗開第2部呢啲已經唔使講; <br />\n係咁出上課不要系同玩返哈棒呢啲唔需要合理性嘅超暴走向嘅小說; <br />\n蟬堡開咗個頭但又冇哂聲氣, 但都恐本身又未出完; <br />\n報告老師個劇情好好, 但電影唔叫好唔叫坐, 小說版反而係電影之後先後補, 我覺得係衰喺個名太on9同埋冇小說做底;<br />\n殺手本身個世界觀仲有好多嘢講+九把刀話過佢係有鋪排過, 所以後期嘅殺手「主線劇情」唔會點差, 但睇得出用字/ 人物描寫/ 細嘅情節鋪排係回塘得好緊要; <br />\n同埋佢個心去咗拍戲同湊仔, 咁作為讀者+fans又真係覺得迫唔落"},{"pid":"71454f82d56991bf6ea4be4ed0c40a5ea2c9a168","tid":2084913,"uid":80381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:35:48.000Z","msg":"寓言殺手先正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"369fbc684f243b2a277143749ab6bc9cb18d83ba","tid":2084913,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T11:36:47.000Z","msg":"九把刀都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bea7776b5bcd7da966bce66cbae4c0532b1eaf74","tid":2084913,"uid":324936,"like":0,"dislike":44,"score":-44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T12:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cz4Y9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cz4Y9e.jpg&h=6a76c8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cz4Y9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cz4Y9e.jpg&h=6a76c8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cz4Y9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cz4Y9e.jpg&h=6a76c8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cz4Y9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1Cz4Y9e.jpg&h=6a76c8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1Cz4Y9e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg